title: Super Natural
description: This supermarket provides all organic fruit and vegetables. Also sells other health products, some of which are organic and some not. Also, eco-toiletries and cleaning products, nappies and more. Has little cafe with selected drinks, pastries and more. Carries a variety of vegan groceries and products. 2015 reported its outlet at R Turiassu 1 645, Perdizes had shut.
